<codeline><highlight class="normal">&lt;a<sp/>href=&quot;https://github.com/radj307/volume-control/releases&quot;&gt;&lt;img<sp/>alt=&quot;GitHub<sp/>tag<sp/>(latest<sp/>by<sp/>date)&quot;<sp/>src=&quot;https://img.shields.io/github/v/tag/radj307/volume-control?color=e8e8e7&amp;label=Latest%20Version&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=e8e8e7&amp;style=for-the-badge&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a<sp/>href=&quot;https://github.com/radj307/volume-control/releases&quot;&gt;&lt;img<sp/>alt=&quot;Downloads&quot;<sp/>src=&quot;https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/radj307/volume-control/total?color=e8e8e7&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=e8e8e7&amp;style=for-the-badge&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</highlight></codeline>
